<text id="75810010">You, approaching Eleum Loyce,</text>
<text id="75810011">Turn back.</text>
<text id="75810012">The old Chaos hungers still.</text>
<text id="75810013">This dead city has nothing to offer.</text>
<text id="75810014">Go back.</text>
<text id="75810015">Do not seek the old Chaos,
nor its twisted flame.</text>
<text id="75810016">%null%</text>
<text id="75810017">%null%</text>
<text id="75810018">%null%</text>
<text id="75810019">%null%</text>
<text id="75810020">It was Aava that found you.</text>
<text id="75810021">The King's orders burden the poor thing yet.</text>
<text id="75810022">But without the sign, you will be repelled.</text>
<text id="75810023">You must turn back.</text>
<text id="75810024">%null%</text>
<text id="75810025">%null%</text>
<text id="75810026">%null%</text>
<text id="75810027">%null%</text>
<text id="75810028">%null%</text>
<text id="75810029">%null%</text>
<text id="75810030">Go back.</text>
<text id="75810031">Aava is watching.</text>
<text id="75810032">Go back.</text>
<text id="75810033">%null%</text>
<text id="75810034">%null%</text>
<text id="75810035">%null%</text>
<text id="75810036">%null%</text>
<text id="75810037">%null%</text>
<text id="75810038">%null%</text>
<text id="75810039">%null%</text>
<text id="75810040">Poor Aava, do you miss your king?</text>
<text id="75810041">One without the sign has arrived.</text>
<text id="75810042">Do be merciful, and end things swiftly.</text>
<text id="75810043">%null%</text>
<text id="75810044">%null%</text>
<text id="75810045">%null%</text>
<text id="75810046">%null%</text>
<text id="75810047">%null%</text>
<text id="75810048">%null%</text>
<text id="75810049">%null%</text>
<text id="75810050">Turn away.</text>
<text id="75810051">And never look back.</text>
<text id="75810052">No one must ever find
that which is sheltered in Eleum Loyce.</text>
<text id="75810100">You've escaped Aava's jaws,
and reached this forbidden land.</text>
<text id="75810101">Who are you?</text>
<text id="75810102">%null%</text>
<text id="75810103">%null%</text>
<text id="75810104">%null%</text>
<text id="75810105">%null%</text>
<text id="75810106">%null%</text>
<text id="75810107">%null%</text>
<text id="75810108">%null%</text>
<text id="75810109">%null%</text>
<text id="75810110">To think Aava could be bested...</text>
<text id="75810111">Who are you?</text>
<text id="75810112">%null%</text>
<text id="75810113">%null%</text>
<text id="75810114">%null%</text>
<text id="75810115">%null%</text>
<text id="75810116">%null%</text>
<text id="75810117">%null%</text>
<text id="75810118">%null%</text>
<text id="75810119">%null%</text>
<text id="75810120">The frozen knights of Eleum Loyce.</text>
<text id="75810121">You have restored their purpose.</text>
<text id="75810122">Who are you, truly?</text>
<text id="75810123">%null%</text>
<text id="75810124">%null%</text>
<text id="75810125">%null%</text>
<text id="75810126">%null%</text>
<text id="75810127">%null%</text>
<text id="75810128">%null%</text>
<text id="75810129">%null%</text>
<text id="75810130">This land is barren,</text>
<text id="75810131">Cursed, by the old Chaos.</text>
<text id="75810132">It gave birth to atrocities,
and the people fled in fear.</text>
<text id="75810133">Until our lord, the Ivory King, came.</text>
<text id="75810134">%null%</text>
<text id="75810135">%null%</text>
<text id="75810136">%null%</text>
<text id="75810137">%null%</text>
<text id="75810138">%null%</text>
<text id="75810139">%null%</text>
<text id="75810140">My dear lord, a most true king.</text>
<text id="75810141">It was with his magnificent soul
that he built Eleum Loyce...</text>
<text id="75810142">...and contained the spread of Chaos.</text>
<text id="75810143">But the Chaos would not be sated,
and the King gave his own soul.</text>
<text id="75810144">%null%</text>
<text id="75810145">%null%</text>
<text id="75810146">%null%</text>
<text id="75810147">%null%</text>
<text id="75810148">%null%</text>
<text id="75810149">%null%</text>
<text id="75810150">Inevitably, the King was drained of vigour,
and plunged into the Chaos' heart.</text>
<text id="75810151">Eleum Loyce was frozen in time, its leader lost...</text>
<text id="75810152">I remain here, to contain the Chaos,
honouring my Lord's wishes.</text>
<text id="75810153">Perhaps one day, he will return...</text>
<text id="75810154">I will stay here, until I wither away...</text>
<text id="75810155">There is nothing here,
save that accursed flame...</text>
<text id="75810156">%null%</text>
<text id="75810157">%null%</text>
<text id="75810158">%null%</text>
<text id="75810159">%null%</text>
<text id="75810160">I have but one wish.</text>
<text id="75810161">That my dear Lord might be freed
from that unspeakable Chaos.</text>
<text id="75810162">I haven't the strength to help him myself,
but perhaps one such as you...</text>
<text id="75810163">Though I am yet to know your name,
stranger, will you lend me your strength?</text>
<text id="75810164">%null%</text>
<text id="75810165">%null%</text>
<text id="75810166">%null%</text>
<text id="75810167">%null%</text>
<text id="75810168">%null%</text>
<text id="75810169">%null%</text>
<text id="75810170">Kind visitor, I thank you.</text>
<text id="75810171">Let me open the path to Chaos.</text>
<text id="75810172">And please, do all you can...</text>
<text id="75810173">%null%</text>
<text id="75810174">%null%</text>
<text id="75810175">%null%</text>
<text id="75810176">%null%</text>
<text id="75810177">%null%</text>
<text id="75810178">%null%</text>
<text id="75810179">%null%</text>
<text id="75810180">Then be gone.</text>
<text id="75810181">There is nothing here, nothing at all.</text>
<text id="75810182">%null%</text>
<text id="75810183">%null%</text>
<text id="75810184">%null%</text>
<text id="75810185">%null%</text>
<text id="75810186">%null%</text>
<text id="75810187">%null%</text>
<text id="75810188">%null%</text>
<text id="75810189">%null%</text>
<text id="75810190">Stranger.</text>
<text id="75810191">Are you now prepared to plunge into Chaos?</text>
<text id="75810192">%null%</text>
<text id="75810193">%null%</text>
<text id="75810194">%null%</text>
<text id="75810195">%null%</text>
<text id="75810196">%null%</text>
<text id="75810197">%null%</text>
<text id="75810198">%null%</text>
<text id="75810199">%null%</text>
<text id="75810200">Many of Eleum Loyce's faithful knights
followed their Lord into the Chaos.</text>
<text id="75810201">But not one of them returned.</text>
<text id="75810202">The King's dutiful subjects waited
patiently for His homecoming.</text>
<text id="75810203">But it was too long a wait to bear...</text>
<text id="75810204">The knights, reborn, will follow your word.</text>
<text id="75810205">The path to Chaos lies behind you...</text>
<text id="75810206">%null%</text>
<text id="75810207">%null%</text>
<text id="75810208">%null%</text>
<text id="75810209">%null%</text>
<text id="75810210">Many of Eleum Loyce's faithful knights
followed their Lord into the Chaos.</text>
<text id="75810211">But not one of them returned.</text>
<text id="75810212">The King's dutiful subjects waited
patiently for His homecoming.</text>
<text id="75810213">But it was too long a wait to bear...</text>
<text id="75810214">The knights of Eleum Loyce await a new leader.</text>
<text id="75810215">One who will guide them into Chaos.</text>
<text id="75810216">The path to Chaos lies behind you...</text>
<text id="75810300">You've granted my one wish...</text>
<text id="75810301">Now, I have no regrets.</text>
<text id="75810302">I was born amidst the Dark.</text>
<text id="75810303">Long ago, in the depths of the Abyss,
my Father perished.</text>
<text id="75810304">The Dark shattered into tiny pieces,
one of which was me.</text>
<text id="75810305">How frightened I was. A frail thing,
born from but a splinter of Dark.</text>
<text id="75810306">I felt that I might simply disappear.</text>
<text id="75810307">I am, in fact, the incarnation of
my Father's fears.</text>
<text id="75810308">I sought an anchor, and I saw
that the King of this land was strong.</text>
<text id="75810309">I sought him only to sustain myself,
to smother my fears...</text>
<text id="75810310">Now, I realise that he may have known all along.</text>
<text id="75810311">I was born of fear,
and my Lord provided comfort.</text>
<text id="75810312">And so here I remain, heiress to my Lord's wishes,
watching over Chaos...</text>
<text id="75810313">...until the end of time.</text>
<text id="75810314">...until I wither away.</text>
<text id="75810315">%null%</text>
<text id="75810316">%null%</text>
<text id="75810317">%null%</text>
<text id="75810318">%null%</text>
<text id="75810319">%null%</text>
<text id="75810320">The knights of Eleum Loyce
were swallowed by the Chaos...</text>
<text id="75810321">...where their souls still remain.</text>
<text id="75810322">I pray for their deliverance...</text>
<text id="75810323">%null%</text>
<text id="75810324">%null%</text>
<text id="75810325">%null%</text>
<text id="75810326">%null%</text>
<text id="75810327">%null%</text>
<text id="75810328">%null%</text>
<text id="75810329">%null%</text>
<text id="75810330">I sense a knight's joyous elation.</text>
<text id="75810331">Kind visitor, please accept my gratitude.</text>
<text id="75810332">%null%</text>
<text id="75810333">%null%</text>
<text id="75810334">%null%</text>
<text id="75810335">%null%</text>
<text id="75810336">%null%</text>
<text id="75810337">%null%</text>
<text id="75810338">%null%</text>
<text id="75810339">%null%</text>
<text id="75810340">My dear Lord has departed.</text>
<text id="75810341">I am left only to fend off the Chaos,
and pray with all my heart.</text>
<text id="75810342">For my dear Lord, and his loyal knights.</text>
<text id="75810343">%null%</text>
<text id="75810344">%null%</text>
<text id="75810345">%null%</text>
<text id="75810346">%null%</text>
<text id="75810347">%null%</text>
<text id="75810348">%null%</text>
<text id="75810349">%null%</text>
<text id="75810350">I sense a knight's joyous elation.</text>
<text id="75810351">Kind visitor, please accept my gratitude.</text>
<text id="75810352">%null%</text>
<text id="75810353">%null%</text>
<text id="75810354">%null%</text>
<text id="75810355">%null%</text>
<text id="75810356">%null%</text>
<text id="75810357">%null%</text>
<text id="75810358">%null%</text>
<text id="75810359">%null%</text>
<text id="75810360">The beings born from shards of Dark...</text>
<text id="75810361">I am not the only one.</text>
<text id="75810362">Even Dark seeks solace, and more so, souls.</text>
<text id="75810363">Magnificent souls...like your own...</text>
<text id="75810364">%null%</text>
<text id="75810365">One day, you may encounter another.
Another being, born of Dark.</text>
<text id="75810366">%null%</text>
<text id="75810367">%null%</text>
<text id="75810368">%null%</text>
<text id="75810369">%null%</text>
<text id="75810370">I sense a knight's joyous elation.</text>
<text id="75810371">Kind visitor, please accept my gratitude.</text>
<text id="75810372">%null%</text>
<text id="75810373">%null%</text>
<text id="75810374">%null%</text>
<text id="75810375">%null%</text>
<text id="75810376">%null%</text>
<text id="75810377">%null%</text>
<text id="75810378">%null%</text>
<text id="75810379">%null%</text>
<text id="75810380">My Father, once human, succumbed to Dark...</text>
<text id="75810381">And later, set in motion its raging advance.</text>
<text id="75810382">The Dark wanders, guided by
its thirst for souls. But perhaps...</text>
<text id="75810383">...man is no different.</text>
<text id="75810384">%null%</text>
<text id="75810385">%null%</text>
<text id="75810386">%null%</text>
<text id="75810387">%null%</text>
<text id="75810388">%null%</text>
<text id="75810389">%null%</text>
<text id="75810390">Kind visitor.</text>
<text id="75810391">I am not the only being born of Dark.</text>
<text id="75810392">You will face hardship like no other.</text>
<text id="75810393">Take this.</text>
<text id="75810394">My sisters are as a thick Dark,
their lust for souls insatiable...</text>
<text id="75810395">May you find the will to resist their desires...</text>
<text id="75810396">Go on, kind visitor.</text>
<text id="75810397">May you reach your journey's end, one day.</text>
<text id="75810500">I sense a knight's joyous elation.</text>
<text id="75810501">Close by, yes, very close...</text>
<text id="75815000">What are you...</text>
<text id="75815001">%null%</text>
<text id="75815002">%null%</text>
<text id="75815003">%null%</text>
<text id="75815004">%null%</text>
<text id="75815005">%null%</text>
<text id="75815006">%null%</text>
<text id="75815007">%null%</text>
<text id="75815008">%null%</text>
<text id="75815009">%null%</text>
<text id="75815010">What do you seek in murder?</text>
<text id="75815011">%null%</text>
<text id="75815012">%null%</text>
<text id="75815013">%null%</text>
<text id="75815014">%null%</text>
<text id="75815015">%null%</text>
<text id="75815016">%null%</text>
<text id="75815017">%null%</text>
<text id="75815018">%null%</text>
<text id="75815019">%null%</text>
<text id="75815020">Oh...my dear Lord...</text>
<text id="75816000">The great door is open.</text>
<text id="75816001">The frigid air of Eleum Loyce
sweeps across the land...</text>
</entries>
